data.description: $10,000 Buyer Incentive to help with closing cost, rate buy-down & etc.! Elegance meets functionality in this captivating two-story home boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, complete with an office and game room. The living room welcomes with soaring ceilings that amplify the sense of space, while vast windows flood the interior with natural light. The kitchen is a culinary delight, showcasing an expansive breakfast bar, island, gleaming granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a gas range. The convenience continues with the primary bedroom located on the first floor, featuring tray ceilings and an ensuite boasting dual sinks and an elongated walk-in shower. Outside, the covered patio overlooks a generous backyard offering ample space for recreation. Don't miss this opportunity - come experience the allure firsthand!
